“Bhikkhus, it is by way of elements that beings come together and unite: those of an inferior disposition come together and unite with those of an inferior disposition.
“Bhikkhus, it is in dependence on the diversity of elements that there arises the diversity of contacts.
“Bhikkhus, it is in dependence on the diversity of elements that there arises the diversity of contacts.
“Bhikkhus, it is in dependence on the diversity of elements that there arises the diversity of contacts; in dependence on the diversity of contacts that there arises the diversity of feelings.
